Docs:
    - Provide basic stylesheet for basic html elements to look exactly the same way across different browsers
    - Allows us to avoid deal issues render in different browsers 
    → https://necolas.github.io/normalize.css/8.0.1/normalize.css
    → line-height: 1.15; (different browsers set different values)
    → margin of <body> to 0; (not space around content of body element)
    Link:
     • <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css" /> => before our custom stylesheets!!